This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it proposes a new feature selection method for predictive models. Additionally, the paper is also relevant to the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with the prediction of complex phenotypic traits using high-density genotyping arrays. The paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE) and game theory (cs.GT) as these fields are often used in genetic trait prediction problems.
